70010000080659.description:
A dynamic action game that immerses the player in the world of tank battles. Take command of a powerful tank and go on exciting missions full of dangers!

Each level is a unique battlefield where the player will have to perform a variety of combat missions. During these missions you will face different types of enemies: from lightly armoured vehicles to heavy assault tanks. Plan your attacks, use cover, strategically manoeuvre and destroy your enemies to achieve victory on every battlefield.

Fight against numerous opponents, complete difficult tasks and prove that you are the real hero of the armoured forces!

GAME FEATURES:
• Stylized cartoon graphics;
• Many levels with varying difficulty;
• Exciting gameplay for fans of tank battles;
• Atmospheric sound.

70010000083445.description:
Your task is to colour a variety of images using a wide range of tools and a palette of bright colours. The game offers many different pictures to colour - choose the images to your liking and start the creative process!

You have a whole arsenal of drawing and colouring tools at your disposal. Each tool can be adjusted in thickness and intensity, allowing you to achieve the desired effect and make your work unique.

This is not only a fun activity, but also a great opportunity to relax and relieve stress. Immerse yourself in a world of colours and fantasy and create your own masterpieces. No matter your skill level, this game will provide you with hours of fun and inspiration!

GAME FEATURES:
• A game for creativity, fantasy and self-expression;
• Many options for images for colouring;
• Relaxing gameplay will allow you to take a break from all your problems;
• A pleasant soundtrack will immerse you in the magical world of colours!
